            "contentType": "interactive",
            "images": [],
            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p>Exiba <code>500</code> dentro da string codificando <code>{500}</code>.</p><code version=\"2\" codelang=\"python\" name=\"script.py\" visible-if=\"always\"><content><text value=\"print(\" /><text value=\"f&quot;I would walk \" /><text value=\"{\" /><text value=\"500\" class=\"number\" /><text value=\"}\" /><text value=\" miles&quot;\" /><text value=\")\" /></content><interactions><interaction type=\"validatedInput\" isDefault=\"true\" startIndex=\"21\" endIndex=\"26\" /></interactions><output><content><text value=\"I would walk 500 miles\" /></content></output></code><p visible-if=\"wrong\">Certifique-se de escolher <code>{500}</code>.</p></body></html>"
          },
          {
            "title": "Example: Variables",
            "id": 79001,
            "contentType": "interactive",
            "images": [],
            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p>Exiba a temperatura atual codificando <code>degrees</code> entre chaves.</p><code version=\"2\" codelang=\"python\" name=\"script.py\" visible-if=\"always\"><content><text value=\"degrees = \" /><text value=\"70\" class=\"number\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"print(\" /><text value=\"f&quot;Temperature: \" /><text value=\"{degrees}\" class=\"subst\" /><text value=\"F&quot;\" /><text value=\")\" /></content><interactions><interaction type=\"fillTheGap\" isDefault=\"true\"><options><option startIndex=\"34\" endIndex=\"35\" /><option startIndex=\"35\" endIndex=\"42\" /><option startIndex=\"42\" endIndex=\"43\" /><option correct=\"false\"><content><text value=\"print\" /></content></option></options></interaction></interactions><output><content><text value=\"Temperature: 70F\" /></content></output></code><p visible-if=\"wrong\">Certifique-se de escolher <code>{</code> seguido de <code>degrees</code> e finalmente <code>}</code>.</p></body></html>"
